{"tid":1514552,"cid":9,"subCid":0,"title":"用twitter 嘅手足留意私隱","createTime":"2019-08-28T19:10:59.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-29T20:10:14.000Z","uid":130698,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"740ab1f0ccb8ed3d8cf222663593ffe406a3e7ae","tid":1514552,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:10:59.000Z","msg":"一年前，話說我用啲廢email 開咗個twitter ac download 埋個app，我都唔知按咗咩setting，可能按咗sign in by Google，按咗幾下同意咁。睇過下twitter 係咩，玩下咁，之後連app del 埋。<br />\n<br />\n今日我開網頁版twitter，見到有通知(鐘) ，撳入去，點解佢會知道我啲phone contacts 用緊twitter?<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e3cmBae.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe3cmBae.png&h=173e5501&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n然後就Google 點del sync contact，setting and privacy, privacy and safety, discoverability and contacts, manage contacts..... <br />\n入到去呆咗，我幾百個電話contacts 都upload 晒畀twitter，仲要我唔記得有呢回事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n於是即刻del 晒所有contacts <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n科技公司無時無刻收集我地啲資料，一個唔小心，轉交咗資料畀第二間保安差啲嘅就洩漏出去。或者政府唔中意你會問公司拎你資料，你就收皮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n依加要研究Google 畀咗啲咩資料人"},{"pid":"5142ec8a9f69065014451298a59ac52023efc1fd","tid":1514552,"uid":130698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T19:18:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KNpPK86.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKNpPK86.png&h=8d2c7576&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"709a26319116289c6515d6a0b50aa46b0252690e","tid":1514552,"uid":268959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T20:03:09.000Z","msg":"好想幫推<